description: USDC is a 100% backed digital dollar minted by Circle and is always redeemable 1:1 for US dollars. By depositing USDC into AAVE, users can earn a variable APY on the USDC. The yield is generated by depositing USDC in AAVE's lending markets and automatically accrued in your account .

USDT is a 100% backed digital dollar minted by iFinex and is always redeemable 1:1 for US dollars. By depositing USDT into AAVE, users can earn a variable APY on the USDT. The yield is generated by depositing USDT in AAVE's lending markets and is automatically accrued in your account.

USDS is a multi-collateral-backed stablecoin managed by Sky that attempts to maintain a value of $1.00 USD. By depositing USDS into AAVE, users can earn a variable APY on the USDS. The yield is generated by depositing USDS in AAVE's lending markets and automatically accrued in your account.

USDS is a multi-collateral-backed stablecoin managed by Sky that attempts to maintain a value of $1.00 USD. The DSR is a special module in the Sky smart contract system that allows USDS holders to receive a share of the revenue earned by Sky. The yield is generated by depositing USDS in the DSR and automatically accrued in your account.
